.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher
House: townhouse, craftsman
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, blood-red
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, cabbage
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person eating cabbage is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the townhouse house##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | iced-tea |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Job           | police-officer | teacher  |
| House   | craftsman            | townhouse    |
| Color   | aquamarine     | blood-red   |
| Food           | raspberry         | cabbage    |
| Transport     | tram           | van      |

